data.thought: S49|H|S47|Domain Phenotype: Data Science - 'Exploratory Data Analyst'. Input: dataset + questions. Process: (1) Profile data (stats, distributions, nulls) (2) Thoughtbox hypothesizes patterns (3) Generates visualization code (4) Container executes, streams plots to Observatory (5) Reasons about findings (6) Generates follow-up analyses. Observable: hypothesis tree, visualization gallery, insight narrative. Human: guides direction, asks follow-ups. Output: comprehensive EDA report + reproducible notebook. 10x faster than manual EDA.
